# 🎮 Keno-Style Weighted Number Generator (1–80)

A web-based interactive Keno-style number generator where users select preferred numbers and influence probability outcomes using a custom weighted system.

---

## 🎯 Features
- Interactive 1–80 selectable grid
- Choose up to 20 preferred numbers
- Weighted probability generator system
- Instant game-style result display
- Reset and replay functionality
- Mobile-friendly UI (game-like experience)

---

## ⚙️ How It Works
The system assigns higher probability weight to selected numbers while maintaining randomness across the full 1–80 pool.

This creates a controlled simulation similar to Keno-style number games.

> Note: This is a simulation tool and does not predict real-world outcomes.

---

## 💻 Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

## 🚀 How to Use
1. Open the website (index.html)
2. Select up to 20 numbers from the grid
3. Click “Generate Result”
4. View weighted outcome instantly
5. Reset and try again

